_sText:
This map is dedicated to my good friend Tyler Benjiman or as css players might know him as Shoes.
This is a very unique map I made based off of Nippers blahhh, you can tell its uniqueness by its random areas like how the trap door at the dance floor leads to an alrenate dimension dance floor were everything is upside down, and by the little desert area under the island, and how the dresser leads to Egyptian style Architecture.
But look for secerets in this map there are a lot of them like the 1 in the terrorist spawn room, you'll have to find it
